\c 3
\s Amadodana kaDavida
\p
\v 1 Njalo la ayengamadodana kaDavida awazalelwa eHebroni: Izibulo nguAmnoni kuAhinowama umJizereyelikazi; eyesibili nguDaniyeli kuAbigayili umKharmelikazi;
\v 2 eyesithathu nguAbisalomu indodana kaMahaka indodakazi kaTalimayi inkosi yeGeshuri; eyesine nguAdonija indodana kaHagithi;
\v 3 eyesihlanu nguShefathiya kuAbithali; eyesithupha nguIthereyamu kuEgila umkakhe\x + 2 Sam. 3.2-5.\x*.
\v 4 Abayisithupha bazalelwa yena eHebroni, lapho abusa khona iminyaka eyisikhombisa lezinyanga eziyisithupha\x + 2 Sam. 2.11.\x*; leJerusalema wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lantathu\x + 29.27. 2 Sam. 5.5.\x*\x + 2 Sam. 2.11.\x*.
\v 5 Lalaba bazalelwa yena eJerusalema: OShimeya loShobabi loNathani\x + 14.4-7. 2 Sam. 5.14-16.\x* loSolomoni\x + 2 Sam. 12.24.\x*, \add bo\add*bane, kuBathishuwa indodakazi kaAmiyeli;
\v 6 loIbihari loElishama loElifelethi
\v 7 loNoga loNefegi loJafiya
\v 8 loElishama loEliyada loElifelethi, abayisificamunwemunye.
\v 9 Bonke babengamadodana kaDavida, ngaphandle kwamadodana abafazi abancane, loTamari udadewabo\x + 2 Sam. 13.1.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaSolomoni
\p
\v 10 Lendodana kaSolomoni yayinguRehobhowamu\x + 1 Kho. 11.43.\x*, uAbhiya indodana yakhe, uAsa indodana yakhe\x + 1 Kho. 15.8.\x*, uJehoshafathi indodana yakhe\x + 1 Kho. 15.24.\x*,
\v 11 uJoramu indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 8.16,24.\x*, uAhaziya indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 8.16,24.\x*, uJowashi indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 11.2.\x*,
\v 12 uAmaziya indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 12.21.\x*, uAzariya indodana yakhe, uJothamu indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 15.7.\x*,
\v 13 uAhazi indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 15.38.\x*, uHezekhiya indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 16.20.\x*, uManase indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 20.21.\x*,
\v 14 uAmoni indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 21.18.\x*, uJosiya indodana yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 21.26.\x*.
\v 15 Njalo amadodana kaJosiya: Izibulo uJohanani, eyesibili uJehoyakhimi, eyesithathu uZedekhiya, eyesine uShaluma.
\v 16 Lamadodana kaJehoyakhimi: UJekoniya indodana yakhe, uZedekhiya indodana yakhe\x + Mat. 1.11.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Njalo amadodana kaJekoniya: UAsiri, uSheyalitiyeli indodana yakhe,
\v 18 loMalikiramu, loPhedaya, loShenazari, uJekamiya, uHoshama, loNedabiya.
\v 19 Njalo amadodana kaPhedaya: OZerubhabheli loShimeyi. Lamadodana kaZerubhabheli: OMeshulamu, loHananiya, loShelomithi udadewabo;
\v 20 loHashuba, loOheli, loBerekiya, loHasadiya, uJushabi-Hesedi, amahlanu.
\v 21 Lamadodana kaHananiya: OPelatiya loJeshaya; amadodana kaRefaya, amadodana kaArinani, amadodana kaObhadiya, amadodana kaShekaniya.
\v 22 Lamadodana kaShekaniya: UShemaya. Lamadodana kaShemaya: OHathushi loIgali loBariya loNeyariya loShafati, ayisithupha.
\v 23 Njalo amadodana kaNeyariya: OEliyohenayi loHizikiya loAzirikamu, amathathu.
\v 24 Njalo amadodana kaEliyohenayi: OHodaviya loEliyashibi loPelaya loAkubi loJohanani loDelaya loAnani, ayisikhombisa.